|--------------------------------|-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|---------------------------------------|
| OPEC+ Production Restraint      | Deliberate slow increase in oil output post-pandemic                                             | Elevated crude oil and gasoline prices|
| U.S. Production & Refinery Cuts| Pandemic-induced refinery closures and production cuts                                           | Reduced supply, tighter market        |
| Demand Rebound                 | Increased travel and economic activity post-COVID                                               | Higher consumption, price pressure    |
